{"tid":981601,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"疑情緒受困　17歲青年大埔墮斃","createTime":"2019-01-14T12:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T14:20:11.000Z","uid":160807,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"756ad97a1c2b50512a59472fe3b9ab30f90fd138","tid":981601,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:04:18.000Z","msg":"下午3時許，一名17歲黎姓青年自大埔翠和里一大廈天台墮下，昏迷送院搶救不治。警方封鎖現場展開調查，檢獲遺書，相信案件無可疑。黎的死因有待驗屍確定。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，事主就讀中六，近月患上情緒病，友人昨透過電話Whatsapp聯絡不果。黎疑情緒受困，今午在上址一躍而下。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線<br />\n<br />\n生命熱線：2382 0000<br />\n<br />\n撒瑪利亞防止自殺會：2389 2222<br />\n<br />\n社會福利署：2343 2255<br />\n<br />\n明愛向晴軒：18288<br />\n<br />\n年輕人專線<br />\n<br />\n香港輔導及心理學會：WhatsApp熱線6218 1084 (提供英語及粵語專業輔導服務)<br />\n<br />\n生命熱線：青少年生命專線 2382 0777<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190114/s00001/1547462586866/%E7%96%91%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92%E5%8F%97%E5%9B%B0-17%E6%AD%B2%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E5%A2%AE%E6%96%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190114%2Fs00001%2F1547462586866%2F%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%25B7%2592%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%259B%25B0-17%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%2594%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E6%2596%2583&d=TXUNqOKSaOu0L9ZIy7QkrARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=29e426cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190114%2Fs00001%2F1547462586866%2F%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%25B7%2592%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%259B%25B0-17%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%2594%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E6%2596%2583&h=0f6846ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190114/s00001/1547462586866/%E7%96%91%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92%E5%8F%97%E5%9B%B0-17%E6%AD%B2%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E5%A2%AE%E6%96%83</a>"},{"pid":